ENTRY       EC 3.5.1.71                 Enzyme
NAME        N-feruloylglycine deacylase;
            N-feruloylglycine hydrolase
CLASS       Hydrolases;
            Acting on carbon-nitrogen bonds, other than peptide bonds;
            In linear amides
SYSNAME     N-feruloylglycine amidohydrolase
REACTION    N-feruloylglycine + H2O = ferulate + glycine [RN:R03579]
ALL_REAC    R03579
SUBSTRATE   N-feruloylglycine [CPD:C02564];
            H2O [CPD:C00001]
PRODUCT     ferulate [CPD:C01494];
            glycine [CPD:C00037]
COMMENT     Hydrolyses a range of L-amino acids from the cinnamoyl and substituted cinnamoyl series. Not identical with EC 3.5.1.14 aminoacylase.
HISTORY     EC 3.5.1.71 created 1992
